      "writtenOn": "2019-02-25T01:21:19Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "why extra indirection? It can be just\n[]*gce.Kind\nand the same for below. Then, code below won\u0027t need awkward config.Kinds.kind\n\nditto for the VMs.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 48,
