        "id": 1141499
      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-02-27T03:43:22Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "but it\u0027d make code simpler now.\nAnd if and when the need arises to add another field, to either config, one can choose to either a) add this field as top level to this struct OR use the indirection.\nSo, unless you have new fields to be added in mind, I\u0027d **suggest** (not insist) to keep code cleaner.",
